1.- Set the following variables in your USER_HOME/swissbytes-build.properties file:
jboss.home=/opt/applications/java/jboss-5.1.0.GA/

2.- In eclipse, you need to setup your SWISSBYTES_HOME classpath variable pointing 
to the SBCOMMON's parent folder.

3.- Import the project into Eclipse

4.- Check-Out sbcommon and maintain this project updated.
5.- You can use the following targets:
	* ant clean //clean the project
	* ant explode //send last changes to your jboss server
	* ant reexplode //send everything to you jboss server
	* ant generateEntities //generate the entities